{"tid":1561706,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拍「電視認罪」央視女主播面臨國際制裁","createTime":"2019-09-11T16:46:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T17:45:25.000Z","uid":56533,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6839654c60165098f0685b1a2a1277a54325a52a","tid":1561706,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/2019/new/sep/11/images/bigPic/600_264.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2019%2Fnew%2Fsep%2F11%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F600_264.jpg&h=cb7304c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台（RFA）報導，人權組織「保護衛士」（Safeguard Defenders）準備向美國、英國、加拿大和英屬直布羅陀等7國及地區申請，依據美國「全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法」及各國類似法律，制裁中國中央電視台女主播、「電視認罪」節目核心人物董倩。一旦各國受理相關指控，董倩將成為央視第一個遭到國際制裁的主持人，面臨海外資產遭凍結、禁止入境等制裁。<br />\n<br />\n「保護衛士」指出，董倩涉嫌與中國警方和國內安全保衛人員合作，為「709大抓捕」案件中至少5名人權捍衛者錄製強制認罪影片，並加以傳播，嚴重侵犯人權。「保護衛士」負責人達林（Peter Dahlin）2016年在中國因涉嫌「危害國家安全」遭警方逮捕，拍攝認罪影片並在央視播出，隨後遭驅逐出境。（編譯孫宇青）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1317097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1317097&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okUv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=9489cce1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1317097&h=65f7dd17\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1317097</a>"},{"pid":"7c99d7b5b57f5ed055e4649474c5d6f38f83a188","tid":1561706,"uid":5682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:46:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 遮打見！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class